{"title":"骨气","authors":["聂焱如"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":12,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"骨气（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"聂焱如"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报载：江西省会昌县杨会发一家，半年时间，挖断了一百一十把铁镐、铁镢，在乱石山中开垦出十五亩地，植上了果树。如今，树绿果香……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比石头还硬的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是钢铁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比钢铁还硬的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是骨气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骨气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是慈爱与真诚的炉火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炼出来的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后经过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"良知的锻打"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才与百折不挠的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"葱郁蓬勃的山的生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了同样的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"质地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"数字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“一百一十”和“十五”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两个平凡却真真实实的数字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在有的人心目中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似乎微不足道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苍白无力"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然而"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是这两个诚诚实实的数字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从坚韧的脊梁中流出来的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通过养育挚爱和真情的脐带"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将山的脉管"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和子孙的脉管"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和谐贯通"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}